trans-unit.source: Represents a container for Web request module configuration elements.
trans-unit.target: 代表 Web 要求模組的組態項目容器。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: This collection holds instances of the [\<webRequestModules\> Element (Network Settings)](../Topic/%3CwebRequestModules%3E%20Element%20\(Network%20Settings\).md) configuration element, which are used to specify modules registered to create requests made with the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> and <xref:System.Net.WebClient> classes.
trans-unit.target: 這個集合會保存的執行個體[ \< webRequestModules\>項目 （網路設定）](../Topic/%3CwebRequestModules%3E%20Element%20\(Network%20Settings\).md)組態項目，可用來指定模組登錄來建立以提出的要求<xref:System.Net.WebRequest>和<xref:System.Net.WebClient>類別。</xref:System.Net.WebClient> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>
